params.name: feature_extractor
params.description: An instance of MarkupLMFeatureExtractor. The feature extractor is a required input.

params.name: tokenizer
params.description: An instance of MarkupLMTokenizer or MarkupLMTokenizerFast. The tokenizer is a required input.

params.name: parse_html
params.description: Whether or not to use MarkupLMFeatureExtractor to parse HTML strings into nodes and corresponding xpaths.
